                "textblock": "Inclusion Criteria:\n\n          -  Age > 55\n\n          -  Current depressive syndrome\n\n          -  Current alcohol dependence\n\n          -  No psychosis\n\n          -  No opioid or cocaine abuse or dependence\n\n        Exclusion Criteria:"
